Output docs/demo-audit.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1240
Set Height 680
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 24
Set Framerate 24
Set TypingSpeed 42ms

Type "# Add --audit for a security report"
Sleep 350ms
Enter 2

Type "npx crxray pifapfmbofjgaenkhhipjhfacfmmhkcp --audit"
Sleep 300ms
Enter

Hide
Type "bash docs/record-demo-audit-play.sh"
Enter
Sleep 9s
Show
Sleep 2s
